 <!-- ... other strings ... -->
 <string name="loading_failed">Failed to load</string>
</resources>
```

What I've done:
1. Created separate composables for each state (Loading, Error, Success)
2. Added the ViewModel to the HomeScreen using `viewModel()`
3. Used a `when` expression to show different UI based on the state
4. Centered all content using `Box` with `Alignment.Center`
5. Added a loading indicator for the loading state
